# Cortex/Knowledge Base Feature

This directory contains the Cortex/Knowledge Base feature implementation with interactive knowledge graph visualization.

## Structure

- `components/` - React components for graph visualization
- `hooks/` - Custom React hooks for graph features
- `stores/` - Zustand stores for graph state management
- `utils/` - Utility functions for graph operations
- `types/` - TypeScript type definitions
- `__tests__/` - Unit and integration tests

## Features

- 3 Visualization Modes: City Map, Blast Radius, Dependency Waterfall
- Hypothesis Mode: Contradiction detection, hidden connections, research gaps
- Entity extraction and relationship visualization
- Graph embedding similarity
- Interactive search and filtering
